{"tid":1527210,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"高中低階反狗鐵行動","createTime":"2019-09-01T09:29:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T09:35:40.000Z","uid":15454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"00c3cb4bef880064089f20260fcaaaed539b983a","tid":1527210,"uid":15454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:29:00.000Z","msg":"好多post都分享點樣不合作搭地鐵<br />\n我個人而言係唔支持嘅<br />\n不過發夢見到原來好多時市民都大頭蝦<br />\n拎銀包出黎拍卡點知原來張卡唔係銀包<br />\n但又唔小心推開左個閘 出閘時又唔記得左去客服度講<br />\n又見到有d某國有時會一家十幾口 一個人拍卡 之後強國排隊式出入大型行李閘機<br />\n仲見到有d parkor 高手練習練得忘我會唔小心露2手<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4885ad1826de304875e1ff4cd9bff2015960b92","tid":1527210,"uid":15454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:29:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfc3c31fedeef6861a5a1a87c8c0705abca50464","tid":1527210,"uid":15454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:29:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f7fc266ad2d9971d53dc5d8f53b8198a9b9272f","tid":1527210,"uid":15454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:29:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b731d95052e380db82c49237004a22a5511b9a","tid":1527210,"uid":15454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:29:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac0f399a10e6cb5a8659a7cb296d29d7dbfac6da","tid":1527210,"uid":15454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:29:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"772b8ea55b7411a35d79b6cc343943457cbb22f0","tid":1527210,"uid":15454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:30:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" c